{"version":3,"term":{"cols":100,"rows":30},"timestamp":1783804714,"command":"./demos/belief-bisect/record-demo.sh","env":{"SHELL":"/usr/bin/zsh"}}
[0.022, "o", "\u001b[1;36m== A belief is a claim about the code, anchored to a commit with evidence ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m$ gpp belief add --claim token expiry is 24h --path auth/** --evidence auth/token.rs:7-7\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.005, "o", "Recorded belief 7aurbnah anchored at cs:ysgeqrpt\r\n  \"token expiry is 24h\"\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m$ gpp belief add --claim auth issues JWTs --path auth/** --evidence auth/token.rs:3-5\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.005, "o", "Recorded belief s36powqo anchored at cs:ysgeqrpt\r\n  \"auth issues JWTs\"\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== Months pass. The code moves on. ==\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.026, "o", "  (3 commits: license header · expiry 24h -> 7d · JWT -> sessions)\r\n"]
[1.001, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== Which beliefs still hold? ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m$ gpp belief stale\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.007, "o", "invalidated      s36powqo  \"auth issues JWTs\"\r\n    2026-07-11  cs:xabtrmyi  stale-candidate  — evidence file auth/token.rs changed (span untouched)\r\n    2026-07-11  cs:6rrvjvul  stale-candidate  — evidence file auth/token.rs changed (span untouched)\r\n    2026-07-11  cs:ccha5suq  invalidated  — scope path auth/session.rs changed; evidence file auth/token.rs deleted\r\ninvalidated      7aurbnah  \"token expiry is 24h\"\r\n    2026-07-11  cs:xabtrmyi  stale-candidate  — evidence file auth/token.rs changed (span untouched)\r\n    2026-07-11  cs:6rrvjvul  invalidated  — evidence auth/token.rs:8-8 changed\r\n    2026-07-11  cs:ccha5suq  stale-candidate  — scope path auth/session.rs changed; scope path auth/token.rs changed\r\n"]
[2.002, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== Which commit killed each one? ==\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m$ gpp belief bisect token expiry is 24h\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.006, "o", "belief 7aurbnah  \"token expiry is 24h\"\r\n  anchored at cs:ysgeqrpt · status: invalidated\r\n  (1 earlier stale signal(s) before the verdict below)\r\n\r\nINVALIDATED  cs:6rrvjvul  2026-07-11\r\n  \"raise token expiry to 7 days\"\r\n  cause: evidence auth/token.rs:8-8 changed\r\n\r\n       6 | }\r\n       7 | \r\n -     8 | pub const EXPIRY_HOURS: u64 = 24;\r\n +     8 | pub const EXPIRY_HOURS: u64 = 168;\r\n"]
[2.001, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m$ gpp belief bisect auth issues JWTs\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.005, "o", "belief s36powqo  \"auth issues JWTs\"\r\n  anchored at cs:ysgeqrpt · status: invalidated\r\n  (2 earlier stale signal(s) before the verdict below)\r\n\r\nINVALIDATED  cs:ccha5suq  2026-07-11\r\n  \"migrate JWT issuance to server-side sessions\"\r\n  cause: scope path auth/session.rs changed\r\n  cause: evidence file auth/token.rs deleted\r\n"]
[2.001, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== Time-travel: the belief set as it stood at the first commit ==\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.005, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m$ gpp belief at ysgeqrptzi4mrxlfyuetz6uplpzqpd5hryfuvuqdzwu7gj4kwdga\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.004, "o", "beliefs as of cs:ysgeqrpt:\r\n  active           s36powqo  \"auth issues JWTs\"\r\n  active           7aurbnah  \"token expiry is 24h\"\r\n"]
[2.002, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m== Deterministic. No LLM. Just the history the repo already had. ==\u001b[0m\r\n"]
